00:44:39,900 --> 00:44:43,100
 nas troje prijatelja na kavi,

884
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:46,960
 i jedan od njih,

885
00:44:46,960 --> 00:44:49,040
 onako kroz priču,

886
00:44:49,040 --> 00:44:49,260
 rekao,

887
00:44:49,260 --> 00:44:50,460
 ni nikad bio u Međugorju.

888
00:44:50,460 --> 00:44:52,540
 Ja rekao,

889
00:44:52,540 --> 00:44:53,260
 ajmo u Međugorju.

890
00:44:53,260 --> 00:44:53,760
 Kažem,

891
00:44:53,760 --> 00:44:54,140
 ajde.

892
00:44:54,140 --> 00:44:55,400
 I sutra dan,

893
00:44:55,400 --> 00:44:56,280
 mi sjedamo u auto,

894
00:44:56,280 --> 00:44:57,260
 bio je petak,

895
00:44:57,260 --> 00:44:58,640
 suboto jutro sjedamo u auto,

896
00:44:58,640 --> 00:45:00,040
 idemo za Međugorje.

897
00:45:00,040 --> 00:45:03,080
 I zapravo,

898
00:45:03,080 --> 00:45:04,900
 on je onako malo i lelujo,

899
00:45:04,900 --> 00:45:06,960
 lelujo šta se tiče života,

900
00:45:06,960 --> 00:45:07,540
 i meni je bilo,

901
00:45:07,540 --> 00:45:08,420
 ajde, nek se ono,

902
00:45:08,420 --> 00:45:09,680
 nek se ispovjedi,

903
00:45:09,680 --> 00:45:11,900
 otičemo na Križevac pod Brdo,

904
00:45:11,900 --> 00:45:13,220
 drugi dan idemo kući.

905
00:45:14,340 --> 00:45:15,060
 I tako je bilo,

906
00:45:15,060 --> 00:45:16,160
 sad idemo mi stati na,

907
00:45:16,160 --> 00:45:18,380
 bili smo na Križevcu,

908
00:45:18,380 --> 00:45:19,460
 vraćamo se na,

909
00:45:19,460 --> 00:45:21,600
 dole na ispovjed,

910
00:45:21,600 --> 00:45:22,620
 i sad,

911
00:45:22,620 --> 00:45:24,320
 ja sam bio i na ispovjedi,

912
00:45:24,320 --> 00:45:26,360
 7-8 dana prije,

913
00:45:26,360 --> 00:45:27,640
 ali on uvijek ima grijeha.

914
00:45:27,640 --> 00:45:30,220
 Ajde, stat ću ja sa njim,

915
00:45:30,220 --> 00:45:30,960
 pa da on ne misli,

916
00:45:30,960 --> 00:45:32,720
 ono kao ja sam njega sad doveo na ispovjedi,

917
00:45:32,720 --> 00:45:33,380
 ajde ti ispovjedi,

918
00:45:33,380 --> 00:45:34,220
 ja ću pit kavule.

919
00:45:34,220 --> 00:45:36,140
 I stanem ja isto u drugi red,

920
00:45:36,140 --> 00:45:37,580
 on u drugi red,

921
00:45:37,580 --> 00:45:40,060
 i dolazimo odmah na red,

922
00:45:40,060 --> 00:45:40,900
 i sad unutra,

923
00:45:40,900 --> 00:45:43,960
 svećernik onako punašniji,

924
00:45:43,960 --> 00:45:44,420
 i malo,

925
00:45:44,420 --> 00:45:47,180
 i sad krenemo mi,

926
00:45:47,180 --> 00:45:50,600
 i krenemo i kaže on,

927
00:45:50,600 --> 00:45:51,360
 odkući ti,

928
00:45:51,360 --> 00:45:52,640
 preko iz Zagreba.

929
00:45:52,640 --> 00:45:53,160
 Kaže,

930
00:45:53,160 --> 00:45:54,860
 ja ću i glave ti čoškaste,

931
00:45:54,860 --> 00:45:55,660
 ti si iz Zagreba.

932
00:45:55,660 --> 00:45:56,080
 Pa reka,

933
00:45:56,080 --> 00:45:56,300
 dobro,

934
00:45:56,300 --> 00:45:57,580
 moj su rodom iz Hercegovine,

935
00:45:57,680 --> 00:45:58,180
 ovaj,

936
00:45:58,180 --> 00:45:59,060
 ali tu smo,

937
00:45:59,060 --> 00:46:02,020
 i sad mi ulazimo već u priču,

938
00:46:02,020 --> 00:46:02,400
 onako,

939
00:46:02,400 --> 00:46:05,460
 ispovjediio sam ja svoje grijehe,

940
00:46:05,460 --> 00:46:08,180
 i sad neformalna priča između nas dvoje,

941
00:46:08,180 --> 00:46:09,340
 on zna ovoga,

942
00:46:09,340 --> 00:46:10,300
 a ja znam ovoga,

943
00:46:10,520 --> 00:46:10,740
 ono,

944
00:46:10,740 --> 00:46:11,600
 ko da smo,

945
00:46:11,600 --> 00:46:13,740
 i sad kaže on meni,

946
00:46:13,740 --> 00:46:15,760
 dobro ili imaš curu,

947
00:46:15,760 --> 00:46:16,200
 je rekao,

948
00:46:16,200 --> 00:46:17,880
 vidim ne nosiš prsten,

949
00:46:17,880 --> 00:46:18,520
 je rekao,

950
00:46:18,520 --> 00:46:19,260
 nemam curu,

951
00:46:19,260 --> 00:46:21,020
 i sad ja njemu ispričam u priču,

952
00:46:21,020 --> 00:46:21,360
 zapravo,

953
00:46:21,360 --> 00:46:21,780
 da sam,

954
00:46:21,780 --> 00:46:22,300
 ovaj,

955
00:46:22,300 --> 00:46:23,540
 da imam crkveni brak,

956
00:46:23,540 --> 00:46:24,060
 da nisam,

957
00:46:24,060 --> 00:46:24,540
 da sam,

958
00:46:24,540 --> 00:46:25,600
 da neću,

959
00:46:25,600 --> 00:46:26,960
 ovaj,

960
00:46:27,020 --> 00:46:28,340
 šest godina više,

961
00:46:28,340 --> 00:46:30,000
 sam sam,

962
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:30,840
 živim čistoću,

963
00:46:30,840 --> 00:46:31,340
 i to je to,

964
00:46:31,340 --> 00:46:31,560
 ne,

965
00:46:31,560 --> 00:46:33,320
 i u trenutku njegov se,

966
00:46:33,320 --> 00:46:34,760
 onako,

967
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:36,320
 od sve te one neformalne priče,

968
00:46:36,320 --> 00:46:37,900
 mi smo se ismijali unutra,

969
00:46:37,900 --> 00:46:43,400
 od njegov lice se onako uozbiljilo,

970
00:46:43,400 --> 00:46:44,980
 i kaže,

971
00:46:44,980 --> 00:46:48,520
 da ću ti,

972
00:46:48,520 --> 00:46:49,400
 ovaj,

973
00:46:49,400 --> 00:46:51,520
 oprost grijeha,

974
00:46:51,520 --> 00:46:53,480
 ako obećaš da ćeš pokrenut postupak,

975
00:46:53,480 --> 00:46:56,640
 pa rekao,

976
00:46:57,020 --> 00:46:57,320
 ok,

977
00:46:57,320 --> 00:46:58,280
 šta ok,

978
00:46:58,280 --> 00:47:01,160
 obećaj da ćeš pokrenut postupak,

979
00:47:01,160 --> 00:47:02,740
 pa rekao,

980
00:47:02,740 --> 00:47:03,160
 obećaj,

981
00:47:03,160 --> 00:47:03,540
 dobro,

982
00:47:03,540 --> 00:47:04,700
 i da mi odrišenje,

983
00:47:04,700 --> 00:47:05,580
 pa rekao,

984
00:47:05,580 --> 00:47:05,760
 ok,

985
00:47:05,760 --> 00:47:07,520
 ono,

986
00:47:07,520 --> 00:47:08,780
 smijali smo se malo prije,

987
00:47:08,780 --> 00:47:13,180
 i,

988
00:47:13,180 --> 00:47:14,060
 ok,

989
00:47:14,060 --> 00:47:15,000
 izađem ja vani,

990
00:47:15,000 --> 00:47:15,760
 i sve je dobro,

991
00:47:15,760 --> 00:47:17,380
 i prijatelji,

992
00:47:17,380 --> 00:47:18,140
 to mi smo se,

993
00:47:18,140 --> 00:47:19,080
 vratili smo se između,

994
00:47:19,080 --> 00:47:19,260
 gore,

995
00:47:19,260 --> 00:47:20,860
 ali ostalo mi to dosta nekako urezano,

996
00:47:20,860 --> 00:47:21,080
 ono,

997
00:47:21,080 --> 00:47:21,380
 mislim,

998
00:47:21,380 --> 00:47:22,020
 ono,

999
00:47:22,020 --> 00:47:23,400
 čem je problem,

1000
00:47:23,400 --> 00:47:23,880
 znači,

1001
00:47:23,880 --> 00:47:24,540
 no,

1002
00:47:24,540 --> 00:47:24,860
 no,

1003
00:47:26,860 --> 00:47:27,600
 i to je,

1004
00:47:27,600 --> 00:47:27,840
 znači,

1005
00:47:27,840 --> 00:47:28,300
 sad bilo,

1006
00:47:28,300 --> 00:47:29,180
 to je ljetno vrijeme,

1007
00:47:29,180 --> 00:47:30,320
 bilo na kraju šestog mjeseca,

1008
00:47:30,320 --> 00:47:31,660
 početak sedmog zapravo,

1009
00:47:31,660 --> 00:47:34,360
 prošli su oni dani u Kazanja,

1010
00:47:34,360 --> 00:47:35,080
 znam da je nije bilo,

1011
00:47:35,080 --> 00:47:35,740
 ovaj,

1012
00:47:36,680 --> 00:47:41,580
 i sad dolazi vam 12. mjesec,

1013
00:47:41,580 --> 00:47:44,020
 i u Palmi,

1014
00:47:44,020 --> 00:47:44,360
 onak,

1015
00:47:44,360 --> 00:47:45,680
 prije,

1016
00:47:45,680 --> 00:47:45,900
 ono,

1017
00:47:45,900 --> 00:47:48,220
 Palmu su stvarno zvali ispovjedavnicu,

1018
00:47:48,220 --> 00:47:49,500
 u grada Zagreba,

1019
00:47:49,500 --> 00:47:51,220
 stvarno bi bilo jako,

1020
00:47:51,220 --> 00:47:53,600
 puno svećenika sa strane bi dolazilo,

1021
00:47:53,600 --> 00:47:53,900
 znači,

1022
00:47:53,900 --> 00:47:54,880
 svake tri,

1023
00:47:54,880 --> 00:47:55,680
 četiri klupe,

1024
00:47:55,680 --> 00:47:57,140
 bio bi pojan svećenik,

1025
00:47:57,140 --> 00:48:00,380
 gdje su bile ispovjede,

1026
00:48:00,380 --> 00:48:01,560
 pogotovo u dane prije,

1027
00:48:01,560 --> 00:48:02,760
 Uskrsa Božeća,

1028
00:48:03,560 --> 00:48:04,060
 i sad ono,

1029
00:48:04,060 --> 00:48:04,960
 tjedna misa,

1030
00:48:04,960 --> 00:48:06,460
 i došl sam ranije,

1031
00:48:06,460 --> 00:48:07,640
 i reko,

1032
00:48:07,640 --> 00:48:08,140
 ajde super,

1033
00:48:08,140 --> 00:48:09,000
 taman je to bilo,

1034
00:48:09,000 --> 00:48:09,300
 ono,

1035
00:48:09,300 --> 00:48:10,560
 pred Božeć,

1036
00:48:10,560 --> 00:48:12,480
 idem se ispovjediti,

1037
00:48:12,480 --> 00:48:14,840
 i u među vremenu,

1038
00:48:14,840 --> 00:48:16,820
 od 7. do 12. sam se ispovjedao,

1039
00:48:16,820 --> 00:48:18,400
 da ne mislite da se ne ispovjedam,

1040
00:48:18,400 --> 00:48:21,960
 ovaj,

1041
00:48:21,960 --> 00:48:27,660
 i stanjem ja u red,

1042
00:48:27,660 --> 00:48:29,800
 dolazim do svećenika,

1043
00:48:29,800 --> 00:48:32,240
 mršavi svećenik,

1044
00:48:32,240 --> 00:48:32,580
 nekim,

1045
00:48:33,560 --> 00:48:34,580
 ja mislim da ono,

1046
00:48:34,580 --> 00:48:37,100
 mislim da nije isusovac sigurno,

1047
00:48:37,100 --> 00:48:39,740
 jer većinu sam ih poznao tamo,

1048
00:48:39,740 --> 00:48:45,880
 ja mislim da možda čak i da nije iz Zagreba,

1049
00:48:45,880 --> 00:48:46,840
 da je bio tu,

1050
00:48:46,840 --> 00:48:48,400
 mršav onako,

1051
00:48:48,400 --> 00:48:49,520
 dosta onako ispijen,

1052
00:48:49,520 --> 00:48:50,520
 i sad stanem ja,

1053
00:48:50,520 --> 00:48:51,580
 ustavljam se sjednem,

1054
00:48:51,580 --> 00:48:53,260
 ili bilo u klupama,

1055
00:48:53,260 --> 00:48:54,620
 kako su bilo je puno redova,

1056
00:48:54,620 --> 00:48:56,120
 i sad pričamo,

1057
00:48:56,120 --> 00:48:56,780
 pričamo,

1058
00:48:56,780 --> 00:48:58,400
 ispovjedimo,

1059
00:48:58,400 --> 00:48:59,900
 i sad je opet je počela priča,

1060
00:48:59,900 --> 00:49:01,740
 i kaže on meni,

1061
00:49:01,900 --> 00:49:04,220
 da reci mi djevojka,

1062
00:49:04,220 --> 00:49:04,660
 rekao,

1063
00:49:04,660 --> 00:49:05,540
 nevam djevojku,

1064
00:49:05,540 --> 00:49:07,680
 i sad opet danjemu priču,

1065
00:49:07,680 --> 00:49:09,500
 koju sam pričao svećeniku u Međugorju,

1066
00:49:11,440 --> 00:49:12,900
 a kaže on,

1067
00:49:12,900 --> 00:49:15,140
 a šta nisi obećao da ćeš to napraviti?

1068
00:49:18,460 --> 00:49:20,040
 i u tom trenutku,

1069
00:49:20,040 --> 00:49:22,000
 i u tom trenutku,

1070
00:49:22,000 --> 00:49:22,640
 onako ono,

1071
00:49:22,640 --> 00:49:23,780
 ko, ko, ko,

1072
00:49:23,780 --> 00:49:25,180
 znači,

1073
00:49:25,180 --> 00:49:27,660
 i mir,

1074
00:49:27,660 --> 00:49:29,820
 i sram u meni,

1075
00:49:29,820 --> 00:49:32,300
 tek onaj trenutak,

1076
00:49:32,300 --> 00:49:33,120
 kad shvatiš ono,

1077
00:49:33,120 --> 00:49:34,720
 da ne ispovjedaš se svećeniku,

1078
00:49:34,720 --> 00:49:35,200
 već Bogu,

1079
00:49:35,200 --> 00:49:36,280
 znači,

1080
00:49:36,280 --> 00:49:39,000
 svećeniku u Međugorju,

1081
00:49:39,000 --> 00:49:39,960
 koji je Franjevac,

1082
00:49:40,340 --> 00:49:41,620
 i ovo je dio Cezanac,

1083
00:49:41,620 --> 00:49:42,760
 u Petrovac,

1084
00:49:42,760 --> 00:49:44,140
 znači,

1085
00:49:44,140 --> 00:49:45,600
 nemaju veze s jedan s drugim,

1086
00:49:45,600 --> 00:49:47,180
 i on mi govori,

1087
00:49:47,180 --> 00:49:49,060
 a šta nisi obećao da ćeš to napraviti?

1088
00:49:50,600 --> 00:49:51,200
 i naravno,

1089
00:49:51,200 --> 00:49:52,000
 u tom trenutku,

1090
00:49:52,000 --> 00:49:52,300
 ja,

1091
00:49:52,300 --> 00:49:55,300
 u tom trenutku,

1092
00:49:55,300 --> 00:49:57,680
 ostajem bez,

1093
00:49:57,680 --> 00:49:58,900
 bez raka,

1094
00:49:58,900 --> 00:50:01,180
 znači,

1095
00:50:01,180 --> 00:50:01,700
 jednostavno,

1096
00:50:01,700 --> 00:50:04,060
 izlazim van iz crkve,

1097
00:50:04,060 --> 00:50:04,660
 ono,

1098
00:50:04,660 --> 00:50:05,900
 toliko onako ojađen,

1099
00:50:05,900 --> 00:50:07,500
 zapravo,

1100
00:50:07,500 --> 00:50:07,820
 ili ono,

1101
00:50:07,820 --> 00:50:09,240
 pristupao sam i toj ispovjedi,

1102
00:50:09,240 --> 00:50:09,920
 i sve mu tome,

1103
00:50:09,920 --> 00:50:10,240
 onako,

1104
00:50:10,240 --> 00:50:10,920
 bez,

1105
00:50:10,920 --> 00:50:11,440
 ono,

1106
00:50:11,440 --> 00:50:12,760
 bez imalo vjere,

1107
00:50:12,760 --> 00:50:13,060
 bez,

1108
00:50:13,060 --> 00:50:13,700
 jednostavno,

1109
00:50:13,700 --> 00:50:13,960
 onako,

1110
00:50:13,960 --> 00:50:14,460
 kao, eto,

1111
00:50:14,460 --> 00:50:15,660
 sad ću ja njemu ispričat,

1112
00:50:15,660 --> 00:50:15,860
 ono,

1113
00:50:15,860 --> 00:50:16,900
 očistio sam sebe,

1114
00:50:16,900 --> 00:50:18,320
 zapravo,

1115
00:50:18,320 --> 00:50:19,300
 nemaš taj osjećaj,

1116
00:50:19,360 --> 00:50:19,980
 zapravo, ono,

1117
00:50:19,980 --> 00:50:21,540
 govoriš pred gospodinom,

1118
00:50:21,540 --> 00:50:22,000
 ono,

1119
00:50:22,000 --> 00:50:23,440
 da gospodinu pričaš,

1120
00:50:23,440 --> 00:50:25,260
 i,

1121
00:50:25,260 --> 00:50:28,100
 nakon,

1122
00:50:28,100 --> 00:50:29,080
 tri,

1123
00:50:29,080 --> 00:50:29,640
 četiri,

1124
00:50:29,640 --> 00:50:31,380
 i dalje sam ja promišljio,

1125
00:50:31,380 --> 00:50:32,300
 da li ću to pokrenu,

1126
00:50:32,300 --> 00:50:32,920
 da li ću,

1127
00:50:32,920 --> 00:50:37,080
 samo tu je i Bog odigro svoju ulogu sa ljudima,

1128
00:50:37,080 --> 00:50:37,540
 naravno,

1129
00:50:37,540 --> 00:50:39,400
 gdje moj jedan prijatelj Dario,

1130
00:50:39,400 --> 00:50:43,240
 jednoj dragoj prijateljici Adranki,

1131
00:50:43,240 --> 00:50:47,140
 zapravo stavio u uho,

1132
00:50:47,140 --> 00:50:47,440
 ono,

1133
00:50:47,440 --> 00:50:48,220
 daj mu,

1134
00:50:48,500 --> 00:50:49,540
 natjere ga da napiše,

1135
00:50:49,540 --> 00:50:50,820
 da napiše tu tužbu,

1136
00:50:50,820 --> 00:50:51,940
 da krene sa,

1137
00:50:51,940 --> 00:50:53,840
 a vjerujte mi,

1138
00:50:53,840 --> 00:50:54,780
 Jadranka je osoba,

1139
00:50:54,780 --> 00:50:55,800
 prostite,

1140
00:50:55,800 --> 00:50:58,060
 Jadranka je osoba koju ne možete reći ne,

1141
00:50:58,060 --> 00:51:00,460
 i koja ne prihvaća išta,

1142
00:51:00,460 --> 00:51:00,660
 ono,

1143
00:51:00,660 --> 00:51:01,760
 ne mogu i neću sad,

1144
00:51:01,760 --> 00:51:05,240
 tako da me ona zapravo natjerala na to da,

1145
00:51:05,240 --> 00:51:08,760
 da pokrenem,

1146
00:51:08,760 --> 00:51:09,920
 zapravo da se pokrenem.

1147
00:51:09,920 --> 00:51:12,360
 I čim sam ja počeo pisat,

1148
00:51:12,360 --> 00:51:13,900
 pisat tu tužbu,

1149
00:51:17,500 --> 00:51:21,980
 2-3 dana jedno prijateljstvo,

1150
00:51:21,980 --> 00:51:23,120
 koje zapravo,

1151
00:51:23,120 --> 00:51:24,440
 ja sam cijelo vrijeme odbio,

